---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Course from "../components/Course.astro";
---

<Layout title="Education - Ali Mansoor">
  <main>
    <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Education & Learning</h2>
    <p class="animate-on-scroll">
      I completed my formal education in Computer Science through quality institutions in Pakistan. My academic foundation began with intermediate studies in computer science, followed by a comprehensive bachelor's degree program where I developed expertise in software engineering, data structures, algorithms, and modern application development.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-on-scroll">
      My coursework covered fundamental computer science concepts including <i>Object-Oriented Programming</i>, <i>Data Structures & Algorithms</i>, <i>Database Management Systems</i>, <i>Software Engineering</i>, <i>Web Development</i>, and <i>Mobile Application Development</i>. I have a strong foundation in mathematics including <i>Calculus</i>, <i>Discrete Mathematics</i>, and <i>Linear Algebra</i>. Beyond formal education, I continuously engage in professional development through online courses and real-world project experience to stay current with emerging technologies and industry best practices.
    </p>

    <section class="courses">
      <Course
        class="animate-on-scroll"
        name="Bachelor of Science in Computer Science"
        university="National University of Computer and Emerging Sciences (NUCES)"
        link={"#"}
        icon="/images/ic_launcher.png"
      />
      <Course
        class="animate-on-scroll"
        name="Intermediate in Computer Science"
        university="Punjab Group of Colleges"
        link={"#"}
        icon="/images/ic_launcher.png"
      />
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: var(--color);
  }
  P {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color);
  }

  .courses {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .courses .animate-on-scroll:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }
  .courses .animate-on-scroll:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
